Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest queue target

Purpose:
  Change the task of an existing active job.

Usage:
  spinedigest queue target <job-id> --task <reading-graph|summary>

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Options:
  --task <task>         New task.

Example:
  spinedigest queue target 75d12f7e --task summary
